# The agent runs on ANY of these — set whichever key you already have.
# Precedence: LLM_BASE_URL > OPENAI_API_KEY > ANTHROPIC_API_KEY > Cloudflare.
# LLM_MODEL overrides the model for whichever provider is picked.
# (No key ships with this repo; nothing here is committed.)

# --- Option 1: OpenAI (default model: gpt-5.4-mini) -------------------------
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# --- Option 2: Anthropic (default model: claude-sonnet-5) -------------------
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Option 3: Cloudflare Workers AI (default: @cf/zai-org/glm-4.7-flash) ---
# Token needs the Workers AI permission.
# CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
# CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
# WORKERS_AI_MODEL=@cf/zai-org/glm-4.7-flash

# --- Option 4: any other OpenAI-compatible endpoint --------------------------
# (Also the way to force a specific provider if multiple keys are set.)
# LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
# LLM_API_KEY=
# LLM_MODEL=

# LLM_MODEL=gpt-5.4-mini
